    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Apartments that offer all the amenities of a normal domestic apartment but in radically reduced size. These have open space for sleeping, working, cooking, and eating. These are typically part of housing projects that are six stories high with 40 units each.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
